OL,3,CGross misconduct proceedings for
OL,4,Cpolice chief after data breach
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FA suspended police chief is to face
OL,8,Fgross misconduct proceedings over an
OL,9,Falleged data breach, a watchdog has
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FRod Hansen, who is the chief constable
OL,13,Fof Gloucestershire Police, will go
OL,14,Fthrough a disciplinary hearing over
OL,15,Fallegations that he failed to
OL,16,Fappropriately act on reports of a data
OL,17,Fbreach.
