OL,3,CGross misconduct proceedings for
OL,4,Cpolice chief after data breach
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,8,FConduct (IOPC) said the allegations
OL,9,Fconcerned whether Mr Hansen did not
OL,10,Fsufficiently act on information passed
OL,11,Fto him in October 2022.
OL,13,FAccording to the IOPC, this related to
OL,14,Fa staff member suspected of carrying
OL,15,Fout an unauthorised search of police
OL,16,Fsystems - and accessing third party
OL,17,Fpersonal data ` linked to a road
OL,18,Ftraffic collision.
