OL,3,CGross misconduct proceedings for
OL,4,Cpolice chief after data breach
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FThe collision took place in September
OL,8,F2022, but concerns over Mr Hansen's
OL,9,Fresponse to the matter only came to
OL,10,Flight in 2024.
OL,12,FPolice and Crime Commissioner Chris
OL,13,FNelson made a referral to the police
OL,14,Fwatchdog in August last year and a
OL,15,Fgross misconduct notice was issued.
OL,17,FMr Hansen was suspended and Maggie
OL,18,FBlyth was appointed interim chief
OL,19,Fconstable. She is now temporary chief
OL,20,Fconstable.
