OL,3,CGross misconduct proceedings for
OL,4,Cpolice chief after data breach
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FAn IOPC spokesman said an
OL,8,Finvestigation concluded Mr Hansen has
OL,9,Fa case to answer for gross misconduct
OL,10,Frelating to challenging and reporting
OL,11,Fimproper conduct; discreditable
OL,12,Fconduct; duties and responsibilities;
OL,13,Fhonesty and integrity; and orders and
OL,14,Finstructions.
OL,16,F"We believe a police disciplinary
OL,17,Fpanel could conclude Mr Hansen didn't
OL,18,Fhandle the matter in accordance with
OL,19,Fthe force's own policy and data
OL,20,Fprotection laws," the spokesman said.
