OL,4,Cpolice chief after data breach
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FA separate investigation into the same
OL,8,Fincident against a different senior
OL,9,Fstaff member concluded they also had a
OL,10,Fcase to answer for gross misconduct
OL,11,Fand will face a separate disciplinary
OL,12,Fhearing.
OL,14,F"It will be for a police disciplinary
OL,15,Fhearing and a police staff
OL,16,Fdisciplinary hearing, respectively, to
OL,17,Fultimately determine whether the gross
OL,18,Fmisconduct allegations are proven,"
OL,19,Fthe spokesman said.
