OL,7,F"All parties have been informed of our
OL,8,Fdecisions, and it will now be for the
OL,9,FOPCC (Office of the Police and Crime
OL,10,FCommissioner) and Gloucestershire
OL,11,FConstabulary, respectively, to
OL,12,Forganise disciplinary proceedings."
OL,14,FMr Hansen became the Chief Constable
OL,15,Fof Gloucestershire Police in 2017. He
OL,16,Fhas a Queen's Police Medal and used to
OL,17,Fserve at Avon and Somerset Police.
